channel.title: Xxx_d - Rapper required [Collab]
channel.description: I don’t want anyone to steal the beat so I’m keeping it until someone DMs me. The kind of rap? I need someone with not a lot of tone, more like “on a single key” rap. After DM I’ll send it to you, and try to make it Top 50 worthy, I’ll mess with the vocals to make it better. I plan on releasing it on Spotify When it becomes free, if you have a distrokid (any distributer) account, then I’ll let you publish. Any questions leave a comment. I’ll try to reply as soon as possible.
